---
import Button from '../ui/Button.astro';
import { APPLICANT } from '../../config/site';
---

<section class="videonote-section" aria-labelledby="video-note-heading">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 id="video-note-heading">About the video ask</h2>

    <div class="videonote-body">
      <p>
        I don&rsquo;t perform well talking to myself on camera. I perform well in actual
        conversations.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you want to see how I think, let&rsquo;s get on a call and I&rsquo;ll walk you through
        anything here live. I&rsquo;ll bring the same preparation I brought to building this, and
        you&rsquo;ll get a much better read on whether we&rsquo;d work well together than a screen
        recording would.
      </p>

      <p>
        The same goes for live whiteboard and algorithmic interviews. I don&rsquo;t have a CS
        degree, and if someone is watching me code under pressure I&rsquo;d
        probably spell my name wrong &mdash; genuinely not my best side. Take-home exercises or
        async work samples give a much more accurate picture of how I actually work.
      </p>

      <div class="videonote-cta">
        <Button href={`mailto:${APPLICANT.email}`} variant="solid" size="md">
          Let&rsquo;s get on a call
        </Button>
      </div>

      <p class="videonote-signoff">
        <cite>&mdash; {APPLICANT.name}, {APPLICANT.title}</cite>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .videonote-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-16);
    background: var(--tone-bg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--tone-border);
  }

  .videonote-section h2 {
    margin-block-end: var(--space-8);
  }

  .videonote-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 68ch;
  }

  .videonote-body p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.3vw, 1.125rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--tone-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .videonote-cta {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-4);
  }

  .videonote-signoff {
    font-size: 0.925rem;
    color: var(--tone-text-muted);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .videonote-signoff cite {
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
